00:30:42.184 --> 00:30:43.668
[Sighs]

613
00:30:43.872 --> 00:30:45.411
_

614
00:30:55.464 --> 00:30:57.052
Papa...

615
00:30:59.623 --> 00:31:02.240
_

616
00:31:02.537 --> 00:31:04.146
_

617
00:31:04.912 --> 00:31:06.326
