966
00:49:45.753 --> 00:49:46.806
Kim?

967
00:49:46.817 --> 00:49:49.259
I'm willing to let bygones be bygones.

968
00:49:49.270 --> 00:49:51.183
And if you agree...

969
00:49:51.503 --> 00:49:54.019
I think we can settle
all this right now.

970
00:49:54.029 --> 00:49:55.799
with a simple handshake.

971
00:49:58.192 --> 00:50:00.219
Where is the... <i>papi</i>?

972
00:50:00.966 --> 00:50:03.418
If I had to do it all over again.

973
